TopicTitle: KSP crashes right after loading completes

Articles.Content:
When I try to load my modded game, it will load with no issues until the loading bar fills up. Then the screen goes black for a moment and then the window closes. I have not been able to get into the game yet.

I have played a modded KSP save before and never ran into this sort of issue.

I'm running version 1.12.4

Reproduction Steps: Open the game, wait for the loading to complete, the game should close without any message or warning.

Player log: https://www.dropbox.com/s/9i58sfx8omwg1oe/Player.log?dl=0
